    'Chromatography Toolbox' for parsing 'Agilent' FID files.")),
    person(given = "Evan", family = "Shi", role = c("ctb", "cph"),
    comment = c("Author and copyright holder of source code adapted from 'rainbow'
    for parsing 'Agilent' UV files."))
